---
import DocsLayout from "../../layouts/DocsLayout.astro";
---

<DocsLayout
  title="Themes"
  description="Customize the look of RefleK's with built-in themes."
  prevPage={{ slug: "mouse-tracking", title: "Mouse Movement" }}
  nextPage={{ slug: "stats-folder", title: "Stats Folder Issues" }}
>
  <h2>Available Themes</h2>
  <p>
    RefleK's includes 10 built-in themes to match your setup. Theme changes
    apply instantly.
  </p>

  <ul>
    <li><strong>Dark</strong> - Default dark theme with blue accents</li>
    <li><strong>Light</strong> - Clean light theme for daytime use</li>
    <li><strong>Dracula</strong> - Purple-accented dark theme</li>
    <li><strong>Gruvbox</strong> - Warm retro dark palette</li>
    <li><strong>Gruvbox Light</strong> - Warm retro light palette</li>
    <li><strong>Nord</strong> - Cool blue arctic palette</li>
    <li><strong>Ocean</strong> - Deep blue oceanic theme</li>
    <li><strong>Solarized Dark</strong> - Popular low-contrast dark theme</li>
    <li><strong>Solarized Light</strong> - Popular low-contrast light theme</li>
    <li>
      <strong>Midnight</strong> - Ultra-dark theme for late night sessions
    </li>
  </ul>

  <div class="image-row">
    <div class="image-container">
      <img
        src="/assets/images/gruvbox_theme.webp"
        alt="Gruvbox dark theme"
        loading="lazy"
      />
    </div>
    <div class="image-container">
      <img
        src="/assets/images/light_theme.webp"
        alt="Light theme"
        loading="lazy"
      />
    </div>
  </div>

  <h2>Changing Themes</h2>
  <ol>
    <li>Open Settings (gear icon in the top right)</li>
    <li>Go to Appearance â†’ Theme</li>
    <li>Select your preferred theme</li>
    <li>The theme applies immediately</li>
  </ol>

  <h2>Font Options</h2>
  <p>You can also customize the font used throughout the app:</p>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Montserrat</strong> - Clean, modern sans-serif (default)</li>
    <li><strong>Inter</strong> - Highly legible interface font</li>
    <li>
      <strong>JetBrains Mono UI</strong> - Monospace font for a technical look
    </li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Theme Persistence</h2>
  <p>
    Your theme and font preferences are saved automatically and persist between
    app restarts.
  </p>
</DocsLayout>
